Hadson Corp said it intends tofile a registration with the Securities and Exchange Commissionwithin one week covering an offering of 3,750,000 commonshares.    The company had 14,260,000 shares outstanding on December31 and 75.0 mln shares authorized.    It said proceeds of the offering are intended to be used tofinance expansion of existing operations, for acquisitions andfor working capital. Reuter&#3;